@wp.kernel
def rand_expr_mxcjjp(data: wp.array(dtype=float)):
    tid = wp.tid()
    v0 = data[tid]
    v1 = 0.0
    v2 = 1.0
    tmp = 0.0
    tmp = wp.abs(v0)
    v2 = (v1 * ((v2 + 0.00 - v2 + 0.44) - wp.sin(v0 + 0.83)))
    v2 = ((0.69 - wp.cos(v1 + 0.81)) - (wp.sin(v1 + 0.52) / (tmp + 0.24 / tmp + 0.82)))
    v0 = wp.cos((0.81 / (v2 + 0.50 - v0 + 0.63)))
    data[tid] = v0
